Put @oatmeal, rolled/quick oats{0.5%cup} in a #bowl, microwave safe.

Add @cinnamon, ground{1%teaspoon} and mix thoroughly.

Add @raisins{0.5%cup}.

Add @water{1%cup}.

Microwave on high (i.e. default) for ~microwave1{90%seconds}

Stir thoroughly, then microwave on high (i.e. default) for ~microwave2{100%seconds}
